document_data.name: Codscove
document_data.mainbody: '''Codscove''' was a small village located on the island of [[Gwynneth]] within the [[Moonshae Isles]].{{Cite interactive atlas}}{{Cite dungeon/196/Backdrop: The Moonshae Isles}}
document_data.Geography: The village was located along the northeastern coast of the island on the south side of the [[Strait of Oman]] on the [[Codsbay]] just northwest of the [[Codsbay Mire]]. The town was surrounded by the trees of the [[Winterglen]].
